    </section> 
    
    {% include "partials/components/membership.njk" %}
    
    <section class="[ post-list ] [ pad-top-700 pad-bottom-300 ]">
      <div class="[ inner-wrapper ] [ sf-flow ]">
        <h2>Shelter Rental</h2>
        <p>Starting May 9 at 8am, you are able to reserve the Pool Shelter on the lower deck and the Shelter area on the upper deck by the Diving Boards. There is a $40 rental fee for the Lower Deck Shelter.  There will not be a charge if you reserve the Upper Deck Shelter.  There are two sessions for rental (11:00-3:30) and (4:00-9:00).  You can only reserve one of the sessions per day.</p>
      </div>    
    </section>
        
    <section class="[ post-list ] [ pad-top-700 pad-bottom-300 ]">
      <div class="[ inner-wrapper ] [ sf-flow ]">
