        <p>You can find information about the swim club, such as our bylaws, on our 
        <a href="https://beechwoodswimclub.us18.list-manage.com/track/click?u=d2234782ae340940dd72dad5c&id=9c3f5b098d&e=c702d2f988">website</a>. Going 
        forward, the most current information such as closures due to weather and things of that nature are posted on our 
        <a href="https://beechwoodswimclub.us18.list-manage.com/track/click?u=d2234782ae340940dd72dad5c&id=84c6927ff3&e=c702d2f988">Facebook page</a>. Follow 
